Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,RO-ED2,,0,0,0,,
Comment: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:05.70,TR-ED2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Nunca contei uma mentira
Comment: 0,0:00:06.01,0:00:08.70,TR-ED2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Nunca me arrependi de nada
Comment: 0,0:00:09.13,0:00:11.60,TR-ED2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Aqueles momentos foram reais?
Comment: 0,0:00:11.92,0:00:14.52,TR-ED2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Não esqueço o dia em que te conheci
Comment: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:17.56,TR-ED2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Nunca mais me sentirei só
Comment: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:20.00,TR-ED2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Você foi a única pessoa
Comment: 0,0:00:20.79,0:00:23.35,TR-ED2,,0,0,0,karaoke,A primeira a me amar de verdade
Comment: 0,0:00:23.61,0:00:26.48,TR-ED2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Isso. Só você. Só o seu coração
Comment: 0,0:00:26.74,0:00:29.40,TR-ED2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Você me deu asas
Comment: 0,0:00:29.70,0:00:32.40,TR-ED2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Quando eu nem sabia voar
Comment: 0,0:00:32.66,0:00:35.32,TR-ED2,,0,0,0,karaoke,E foi você também
Comment: 0,0:00:35.46,0:00:38.30,TR-ED2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Quem me deu liberdade
Comment: 0,0:00:38.67,0:00:41.30,TR-ED2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Quando fecho os olhos, posso te ver
Comment: 0,0:00:41.59,0:00:44.25,TR-ED2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Aqui do meu lado
Comment: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:47.23,TR-ED2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Toda vez que o vento sopra
Comment: 0,0:00:47.31,0:00:51.07,TR-ED2,,0,0,0,karaoke,O mundo todo parece sorrir
Comment: 0,0:00:53.96,0:00:56.40,TR-ED2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Mesmo que não esteja aqui
Comment: 0,0:00:56.91,0:00:59.20,TR-ED2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Mesmo que eu feche os olhos e você desapareça
Comment: 0,0:00:59.34,0:01:03.20,TR-ED2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Ainda posso te sentir...
Comment: 0,0:01:03.75,0:01:04.70,TR-ED2,,0,0,0,karaoke,No vento...
Comment: 0,0:01:05.27,0:01:08.05,TR-ED2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Você me deu asas
Comment: 0,0:01:08.24,0:01:10.90,TR-ED2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Quando eu nem sabia voar
Comment: 0,0:01:11.18,0:01:16.80,TR-ED2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Me ensinou o verdadeiro significado de amar
Comment: 0,0:01:17.12,0:01:19.80,TR-ED2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Quando vejo o céu azul em seus olhos
Comment: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:22.75,TR-ED2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Após uma chuva repentina
Comment: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:25.70,TR-ED2,,0,0,0,karaoke,Os nossos sorrisos se encontram
Comment: 0,0:01:26.00,0:01:29.94,TR-ED2,,0,0,0,karaoke,E um grande arco-íris floresce
